title: Sel Sel Lyrics Kaakk Muttai Song Lyrics
stanzas:
Kaakka Muttai Sel Sel Song Lyrics
Singer(s): Sathya Prakash
Music: GV Prakash,

Chal chalae
chal chalae chal chal.
chare chal chalae
chal chalae chal.

Chal chalae chal chalae
siragai virithu sel.
Chal chalae chal chalae
kaattril yaeri sel.

Po po, vazhve
kaakkaa mutta thaan.
kottai vittae
potta satta thaan.

Mazhai veyil
rendum engal
annan thambi thaan.
Natchathiram varuvadhu
nammai nambi thaan.

ingae vali yaavum
nerillai sandhula
pondhula po po
po poda po poda
pudhu inbam thaedi po
kanpaarkkum yaavum
un sondham endrenni po
innum melae po.

Thooral vandhaalingae
koni kudaiyaagumey.
oru quater bottle-lai
vilakkaai maattri
iruttai ottiduvom.

ada yaar veedum
nam veedu ena enni
vazhugirom po po
po  poda po poda
pudhu inbam thaedi po
kanpaarkkum yaavum
un sondham endrenni po
innum melae po.

Touser dhapaal petti
dhosthu aattu kutti.
dhinam anjae rupaai
kidachaa podhum
hero naangaladaa.

rathiri engal
kachchaerikku
vandugal paadumadaa
ada ration card
adhil engal
naai per serthiduvom.

po po
po  poda po poda
pudhu inbam thaedi po
kanpaarkkum yaavum
un sondham endrenni po
innum melae po.

kaattril yaeri sel.
